Events.Text: Welcome to Amorous!░ Hottest club in town.░ I'm Jax and I'll be your Beverage Artisan this evening. What can I do for you?
Events.Title: Jax

Choices.Text: I'd like to order a drink.

Events.Text: As I slid into one of the stools,░ he set a glass in front of me.░ I think I'd like a drink.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: What did you have in mind?
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: Here you go! Anything else?
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: Still not sure about the club or its residents,░ I decided on getting something sensible. Just a ginger ale for now,░ thanks.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Living dangerously, ░I see.░ Or perhaps "designatedly".
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: Just ribbing you. ░One ginger ale coming up!
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: With a rather surprising flourish,░ he slid his hand against the glass and rolled it between each finger before catching it by the base. ░He brought both back up to the counter, ░flipping the glass over while still holding it and shot a steady stream into it like he was firing a pistol.░He released the glass and, drawing his hand back,░ drew a rag from his cuff and wiped the bar in front of me clean.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Your drink.
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: Wow!░ That was quite the show!
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Always happy to serve an appreciative customer!░ Is there anything else I can do for you?
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: I'm good.░ Thanks!░ I picked up my drink and wandered away from the bar.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Well, you could start by telling me how you learned how to do that! I sipped at my drink as he chuckled and leaned forward on the bar.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Drive, determination,░ months of nothing better to do and the need for tips to feed my eating and rent-paying habits.
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: He winked at me and stood back up.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Anything else I can do for you?
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: Yeah.░ You can tell me a little more about yourself.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: I thought you came here to have fun,░ not just chat up the bartender.░ Not much to tell,░ honestly.░ What you see is what you get!
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: Seems like despite his friendly demeanor,░ he's hesitant to talk about himself.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: How about I start?░ My name's %playername% and I'd like to get to know you better.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Sorry.░  I ...░ just being a bartender tends to get you quite a bit of unwanted attention.
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: You already know my name,░ but,░ it's nice to meet you %playername%.░ Got to say,░ you're already not what I expected in a customer!
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: You're not quite what I expected in a bartender.░ Not that I've met my other bartenders.░ Or gone to many other bars.░ I stopped myself and took a breath.░ What I'm trying to say is,░ I'd like to know more about you.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: There isn't much to tell, ░really.░ Late nights working at the club don't really leave me much time to do anything else.░ Everyone else is either at work or asleep.
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: Why bartending then?░ I mean,░ you're clearly amazing at it but...░ I trailed off as I saw his expression change.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: It's ... a long story.░ Not something for light conversation on a fun night.
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: He's still very guarded. ░Maybe I shouldn't press him.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Did something happen?░ Are you in hiding?░ Is someone after you?░ You can't just leave me hanging like this!
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: I can and I'm going to.░ I'm paid to serve you drinks and that's it,░ got it?
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: His expression slowly softened but I could still feel a cold chill coming off him.░ I think I pushed too hard.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Got some other customers to make sure they don't die of thirst.░ Just let me know if you need a refill!
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: Wait!░ I held up my hand and waved him back down.░ He reluctantly turned to speak to me again.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Can I help you?
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: I bit my lip for a moment.░ Sorry.░ I went too far.░ My bad.░ I just didn't want to leave it where it was. His eyes watched me for a long moment before he nodded.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Fair enough.░ I do get a little ...░ sensitive at times.░ We've all got our issues and I wind up shouldering quite a few of them from other people back here.
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: That said,░ no point is adding to them.░ Anything else I can help you with?
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: Anything in particular?
Events.Title: Jax

Choices.Text: Do you know much about the patrons here?

Events.Text: I've never been here before.░ A friend convinced me to come and then kinda left me in the lurch.░ What's a night here like?
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Well, there's the usual club crew;░ looking to have a good time in any way possible.░ The dance floor is usually pretty packed,░ but most people are looking for someone to connect with.░ Either that or they're telling me their problems.░ And of course, the drinks are all top notch!
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: Hope that helps!░ Need anything else?
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: What brought you here?
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: A friend of mine really wanted to come here.░ I wasn't completely sure I wanted to come along but he's persuasive.░ Of course now I'm sitting here,░ talking with someone I've just met.░ I felt my cheeks flush.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Hey, it comes with the job.
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: That said,░ we don't really ever get to know people until we sit down and talk with them.░ So in the interest of making you feel a little more comfortable,░ since you know my name,░ what's yours?
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: %playername%.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Nice to meet you, %playername%.░ What do you do when not indulging chatty bartenders?
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: My job mostly keeps me busy.░ The hours are a little more regular but I don't get tips and I rarely get anything to drink other than water.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Well,░ despite the more active crowd currently,░ I can assure you that my job gets pretty boring as soon as the club empties.░ It's also much harder to keep yourself motivated to clean when it's three in the morning.
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: I should probably get to the rest of the customers before they start complaining.░ Always has a negative effect on tips.░ Let me know if you need anything else.
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: Nice to meet you Jax.░ Maybe I'll drop back by for a drink.░ He winked at me and smiled.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: I'll hold you to that!
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: Usually I hang out with my friend,░ play video games and generally find fun ways to waste time.░ Nothing as exciting as bartending, I'm sure.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Believe me.░ It's the kind of excitement that wears thin after a while.░ Don't get me wrong,░ I wouldn't be doing it if I didn't love it but ...
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: Never mind me. Video games,░ huh?░ Pretty popular pastime nowadays.░ What kind do you play?
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: I mostly play action games.░ Something to really get the adrenaline pumping.░ Nothing like facing down a challenge and having nothing but your reflexes to keep you going.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Sounds like you enjoy being able to prove yourself.
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: Guess so.░ It's fun to see just what you can do given the opportunity.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Well, you came to the right place to find opportunities.░ Sadly, I'm on the clock and should get back.░ Can I get you a drink before I go?
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: I enjoy RPGs,░ things that really make you think.░ Tactics are all well and good,░ but give me a good,░ solid story any day!
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: I hear lots of stories in my line of work.░ Some are enjoyable,░ others not so much.
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: I suppose it depends on the person telling them.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Very true!░ That said,░ we've got a whole club of potential stories out there.░ Who knows what you might find.░ However,░ our story ends unless you're intending on buying a drink.░ Sadly, I'm on the clock.░ Can I get you something?
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: I'm really into these new Dating Sims.░ They seem kind of interesting.░ Being able to explore characters,░ get to know them better and find out what they're like.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Huh. Dating Sims?░ Aren't those mostly text based?
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: Sometimes.░ But they can have really engrossing stories and conversations.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Guess that could be fun. I do like to chat with people.░ Unfortunately, I'm on the clock and my boss doesn't like it when I spend all my time chatting.░ Can I get you a drink?
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: Just had quite a bit on my mind.░ Though I could use a change of scene.░ My friend agreed and suggested we come here.░ I suppose it's just a little overwhelming? I chuckled nervously.░ Sorry,░ it's not quite the scene I'm used to.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: It never is the first time.░ Believe me,░ I've seen just about every flavor of person walk through that front door.░ Still,░ maybe you should mingle a little.░ Most of the people here tonight are regulars.░ Who knows, you might meet someone interesting.
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: Thanks!░ I'll take the advice.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: It's why we're all here.░ Just let me know if you need anything else!
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: Maybe so.░ You seem particularly interesting.░ Is that your regular uniform or your own choice?
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: My own choice.░ They are pretty free with the dress code here,░ as you can tell from some of the patrons.░ I like to stand out in my own way from the rest of the crowd.░ Was there a reason behind your outfit?
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: Thought I might be dancing or something.░ Figured it was a good idea to be comfortable.░ Though I can see that's not what most people dressed for.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: True enough.░ Most of the regulars like to show off the assets they have.░ Nothing wrong with being comfortable either,░ I just enjoy riding the edge between classy and risqué.░ Sadly,░ as much as I enjoy talking about clothing,░ I'm on the clock. If you're not going to order,░ I should check in with the other customers.░ Can I get you something?
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: I was coming out to be seen,░ so I figured I should show as much of myself as possible.░ I grinned broadly as I moved to a more flattering view.░ He began to turn a little purple at the cheeks.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: You certainly chose well.░ That outfit looks ...
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: He swallowed,░ adjusted his tie and cleared his throat.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: However,░ you're a customer and I'm still at work.░ Can I get you a drink?
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: Got a little,░ "pent up" energy if you know what I mean.░ It's been a while and I've got the itch to get together with someone for a little casual fun.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Bit of a predator on the prowl,░ eh?░ Much as I hate to see my beloved bar as a meat market,░ I do have to point out a number of choice cuts.░ Quite a few attractive ladies on the dance floor and even a couple of guys,░ if that's the way you swing.
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: I could certainly swing your way,░ if you know what I mean.░ He quirked an eyeridge at me.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: I think I do.░ However,░ I'm your bartender at the moment and it wouldn't be professional.
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: I don't mind you getting a little unprofessional.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Sorry.░ I don't date on the clock.░ Rule number one.░ Can I get you something to drink?
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: Putting on a sly expression,░ I leaned over the counter. That depends on how a handsome reptile like you landed this job and if you might be looking to fill any other openings.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: ... hadn't heard that one before,░ I'll admit.
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: C'mon, blue.░ You, me, the back of my car.░ We can enjoy each other's company all night long.░ You won't even have to wear anything special.░ Or anything at all.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: You seem to have me confused with another type of service.░ I serve drinks,░ I smile and I make sure you don't drive home drunk.░ That's it.░ There are plenty of eager patrons to get your way without pestering employees.
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: What can I do for you?
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: Someone you had in mind?
Events.Title: Jax

Choices.Text: The guy hanging by the elevator?
Do you know anything about the girl in that booth?
The woman in the cocktail dress in the lounge?

Events.Text: Could you tell me more about the punk husky who's hanging around out back?
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text:
I think I know who you mean...
Honestly,░ I don't think they're a patron here,░ we've never spoken.░
I don't think they look like club material,░ I kinda get the stink eye when I go out there...
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: The lion guy back there seems like a cool dude,░ what's he like?
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text:
Dustin?
He seems nice enough,░ though I rarely see him with someone for more than a week.░ He must really like the casual stuff.
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: The cute satyr in the lounge seems lonely.░ Is she nice?
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text:
They don't call her Mystery for nothing!░ Or maybe it was Mercy?...░
You never know who you'll find in Amorous,░ I do know she loves her cocktails.
Events.Title: Jax

Choices.Text: There's a girl by herself at the pool?
The feline guy at the bar?
That about does it for now.

Events.Text: The bunny girl with the glasses seems a bit lost.░ Is she new?
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text:
Remy? You would think so with how quiet she is,░ but she's actually here quite frequently.░
I know she's a little older,░ doesn't play the scene too much,░ let that feed your curiousity!
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: The cat beside me is awfully quiet.░ Is he always like that?
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text:
He's chatty if you grab his attention!░
Somehow he can zone out amongst all this noise and work on his stories.░ His name is Seth and he's writing something,░ that's all I really know...
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: That girl with the golden fur doesn't seem to be having a good time.░ What's up with that?
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Can't say I've seen her around before.░ Maybe it's her first time?░ She came in with a few rowdier girls,░ but she hasn't been too eager to get up and dance or anthing.░ Perhaps go see how her day is going?
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text:
Are all your bouncers dragons?░
He seems nice, a little stoic?
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text:
Makes for a very safe club if I do say so!░
The guy upstairs is Zenith, he's nicer than he looks!░ He's one of our more popular staff members░... for obvious reasons.
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: Considering for a moment,░ I shook my head and smiled.░ I'm alright. Thanks.░ He nodded and stepped back,░ walking down the length of the bar to another couple.░ I sipped my drink and walked back into the main room of the club.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: I think I upset him.░ Maybe I should check out the rest of the club instead.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Sorry.░ I didn't mean to press.░ You seem like a great guy and,░ well,░ I'm out here to meet people.░ I stood up and picked up my drink.░ He hesitated a moment before putting a hand on mine.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: You've got to understand one thing;░ being back here,░ being something for everyone...░ you build barriers.░It's harder to take people at face value sometimes.
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: We both looked at each other for a moment as I considered what he said.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: I stopped,░ placed my drink back on the bar and settled in.░ Too much about this bartender interested me to just let it go at that.░ However,░ I'd have to be a little more reserved with my curiosity.░ I can understand that.░ I'm sure you get more than your share of unwanted conversations.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: There was an awkward pause,░ him absently cleaning the bar with a rag as I sipped at my drink.░ I didn't want to sit in silence but I didn't want to scare him off again,░ so I considered my options.░
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: I smiled back at him.░ It's okay.░ I think I'm going to mingle for a bit but I may drop back by when my glass is empty.░ He nodded and smiled back,░ his colors brightening a little.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Fair enough.░ Can't keep you all to myself,░ after all.
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: His expression briefly shifted as his cheeks grew a rather ruddy purple.░ Adjusting his tie,░ he managed to compose himself back to his regular hue.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Have fun!
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: Clearly you enjoy what you do.░ What brought you to bartending?░ As I sipped my drink,░ I noticed his smile begin to falter.░ He quickly tried to cover up.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Oh,░ the women and the nightlife.░ It's always fun to be able to put on a show and make people's nights░ It's nothing special. Really.
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: Surely you didn't just come here to try to play psychologist to a bartender.
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: He's still very guarded.░ Maybe I shouldn't press him.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text:
To be honest,░ you're not what I expected in a bartender either.░ Cute,░ well-dressed and quite charming.░
 
Are you busy after work?
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Flattering as that is,░ I make it a point not to get involved with customers.░ It gets ...░ messy.
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: I can do messy.░ I might even like messy.░ I smiled broadly until I noticed his expression changing.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: That makes one of us.
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: He cleared his throat a little and put back on a smile.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: You're a nice guy but there's a reason I don't do that.░ Let me know if you need a refill.
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: The look on his face suggested I shouldn't push.░ I nodded and relented.░ I see.░ Well, my loss then.░ It's nice to meet you, Jax. You make a fantastic drink!░ I held up my glass and fished off the last of my drink.░ For a moment,░ I felt his eyes on me and when I looked back down,░ he was still staring at me.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: It's nothing personal.░ I just get those kind of cracks quite a few times a night.░ Comes with the job I guess!░ Do you need a hand with anything else?
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: Sorry,░ This is akward for me.░ I might go check out the rest of the club if thats ok.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Thats all,░ thanks!
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: I sat there,░ bewildered,░ as the drink slowly settled in my glass.░ I wasn't quite sure what had happened but it felt uncomfortable.░ The bartender must have noticed my expression,░ as I watched his brightly colored scales shift to more subdued tones.░ He adjusted his tie and wiped down the bar in front of me.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Sorry. Guess I'm a little too much of a showman.░ Is there anything else?
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: Sorry.░ That's just a bit more than I expected from a simple drink order.░ I tried to cover up my discomfort and took a sip from the drink.░ The bartender smiled meekly and nodded,░ turning towards a new couple walking up to the bar.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Already a little thrown off by the bartender's theatrics,░ I decided it would be better to take my drink and see what else the club would have to offer.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Maybe I came off a little too harsh.░ I held up my hand and motioned the bartender back.░ Sorry.░ Just, not expecting that.░ I felt even more awkward then before.░To his credit, he shrugged it off easily enough and gave me a small smile.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: It's alright.░ My boss isn't always fond of my antics either.░ Thanks, though.
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: I smiled back and placed a tip on the bar counter before picking up my drink and walking back into the club.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: I think we got off on the wrong foot.░ I'm %playername%.░ It's my first time here and I'm just trying to relax.░ He nodded and leaned forward on the bar.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: It's a great place,░ in my opinion and you picked a good night to drop by. ░Plenty of people to meet and,░ if you're more of the quiet type, ░you can always hide here at the bar.
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: We both chuckled and I already started to feel more comfortable.░ He seems like a nice guy.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: No.░ That should do it.░ Thanks for the drink atleast I guess.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Your welcome.░ Have a fun night.
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: I came here to relax and now is a good a time as any to start!░ Looking over the drink menu,░ I considered my options. I'll have something to help take the edge off.░ He looked at me appraisingly for a moment.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: I see you as a beer kind of guy. ░Not enough frog in the face for anything too hoppy.
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: Sorry,░ bartender humor.░ Let me get you a house ale!
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: He disappeared below the bar for a moment,░ rising to produce a pint glass.░ He next slid it under the tap,░ pulling a nice long drought before flicking his wrist and sending the drick sailing in my direction.░ Too surprised,░ I didn't reach out soon enough but found the drink stopped right in front of me without a drop spilled;░ the tip of his tail curled around the base.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: One ale,░ shaken but not stirred.
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: He smiled and released the glass from his prehensile grip before I wrapped my fingers around it.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: After a moment's consideration,░ I decided that if I was going to try something new tonight,░ I might as well be adventurous! I put the drink menu down and smiled at the bartender.░ You know what?░ Surprise me!
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: His smile lit up immediately,░ eyes twinkling with a little mischief.░ Leaning towards me he whispered in a conspiratorial tone.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: You absolutely sure?
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: I opened my mouth to speak when he leaned forward and pressed a finger against his Cheshire-like grin.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Nope!░ Too late!
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: Flicking his wrists to settle his cuffs,░ he began. ░His hands slid beneath the bar,░ wrist over wrist,░ and in a single motion he drew out two bottles.░ Flipping both upside-down and forward he poured a shot of each into the glass before me before flipping them over his fingers like an action movie pistol,░ setting them down on the bar and releasing them.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Next, his hips shifted as I noticed his tail wrapping around the neck of a third bottle;░ lifting it smoothly off the shelf behind him and letting it roll down the full length of his tail to the small of his back.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: His right hand snagged the bottle by the neck,░ bringing it to the front,░ he gave it a quick shake with his wrist before flipping it over his index finger and setting it down with the others.░ With another quick hip shift,░ his tail wrapped around a fourth bottle and launched it into the air.░ My eyes went wide as almost completely through the arc.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: He caught the bottle by the neck and held it an inch or two above the glass before giving it two quick shakes.░ He tossed the bottle back behind him with a grin as it sailed straight back towards his tail tip.░ While it snaked around it, the bottle shifted just enough that I could see it slip.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: His expression went from joy to horror as it smashed into the floor behind him.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Dammit.░ That's going to come out of my check.
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: I sat there,░ staring at my glass for a very long time.░ I still wasn't completely sure what I had just witnessed.░ He had clearly noticed my dumbfounded expression.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: You ok there?
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: I snapped out of my shock and nodded slowly.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Sorry about that.░ I'm a bit of a showman and, well,░ I was excited about trying out something new.░ Probably not the best choice in this situation.░ Still,░ I hope you enjoy the drink.
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: My hand managed to grab his wrist for a moment as he looked back at me.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Sorry. I didn't mean to insult you.░ I released his wrist and he drew it back quickly. Just,░ first time I've been served a drink with such flair.░ I felt a little awkward.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: It's alright.░ Enjoy the drink.░ No charge.░ It was an experiment and I'm just glad you're taking it well.
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: He smiled and walked over to check on the other customers.░ I did notice him keeping an eye on me while I picked up my drink.
Events.Title: %playername%

Choices.Text: Leave it on the counter in disgust

Events.Text: I tipped back the glass and emptied it with a smile.░ Perhaps wasn't the best idea as I felt a little lightheaded.░ I felt myself rock forward and was about to hit the bar when something cushioned my fall.░ Blinking, I looked up to see the bartender,░ with a concerned look on his face,░ and his thick tail under my chin.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: I wouldn't have poured you that if you had that intention.░ That's some heavy stuff.
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: He reached over and poured a tall glass of water,░ setting it in front of me.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: I admire your machismo,░ but drink up and just sit right there.░ If you're intending on leaving anytime soon,░ come back to the bar.░ You're not driving yourself or anyone else home tonight.
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: I tried to object but he was firm about it.░ After the water,░ I was feeling a little better and decided to walk back into the main room to find Coby and move around.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Despite the effort,░ the drink didn't turn out very well.░ With a frown,░ I leave the drink at the bar.░ The bartender seems a little crestfallen but he takes the glass down and empties it into the sink before setting it in pile to be washed.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: My hand went immediately to my wallet and I placed it down on the bar.░ Put it on my tab.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: You sure about that?░ That was a $45 bottle of booze.░ It's not like I'm going to lose my job over it.░ At least, I hope I won't.
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: He looked flustered for a second and composed himself.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: It's my bad.░ Really.░ Job hazard.░ I couldn't ask you to cover this.
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: I smiled.░ It's a good thing you didn't then.░ I laid out a fifty on the bar in front of him.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: You...░ wait...░ wha...░ You're serious?░ I don't...
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: Congratulations are in order.░ You actually got me to shut up for a second.░ I'm just completely blown away by this.
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: It's not a big deal,░ you gave me a fantastic show!░ I mean, wow!░ I didn't even know people could do that kind of thing.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: You're not helping me with the whole looking professional thing here,░ you know?
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: He grinned and put away the remaining bottles.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Drink's on me.░ Totally.░ You've just been too sweet of a customer to charge for one of my experiments.░ I'll get you your change.
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: I thanked him for the five dollars back and slipped my drink for a moment.░ Despite working with other customers,░ I could see him watching my reaction out of the corner of my eye.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: You earned it. All of it.░ Fair and square.░ That was mindblowing!
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Your unabashed admiration is thanks enough but I do think you forgot something.
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: I furrowed a brow as I put my hand back on my wallet.░ He smiled and slid a slip of paper over to me.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: I think you'll know what to do with that.
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: As he moved to the next customer I flipped the paper over to see a phone number with his name,░ in an embellished script, below it.░ I slid the paper into my pocket.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: I'll be able to call Jax after tonight to meetup again sometime!
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: I nearly screamed over the bar as I jumped out of my stool. Holy shit!░ You could have killed me!░ What the hell were you thinking?
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Look, I'm sorry.░ I just like to put on a bit of a show.░ Drink's on me. Relax.░ I'll just get one of the other bartenders to help you if you need anything.
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: I probably shouldn't bother him further with my service.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Nevermind,░ thanks.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: My hand barely touches the counter before the bartender is right in front of me.░ From here I can see that his uniform,░ while dapper,░ is clearly tailored for the club.░ His sleeveless vest and cuffed wrists are capped by a revealing tuxedo styled brief as well.░ Despite his state of near undress,░ he seems quite chipper and buffs down the counter in front of me with a rag.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Welcome to Amorous!░ Hottest club in town.░ I'm Jax and I'll be your Beverage Artisan this evening.
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: He winks at me before continuing.
Events.Title: %playername%

Choices.Text: I'd like to order a drink.

Events.Text: Anyone else you want the scoop on?
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text:
Listen...░
You don't usually do this,░ and I'm not pushing or anything...░ but you seem kinda sweet.░ I'd love the chance to chat when you're not on the clock.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text:
...░

You know what?░ Sure.░ Rules are made to be broken, right?░ Just don't make me regret this...
Events.Title: Jax

Events.Text: <i>He smiled and scribbled something down on a small notepad before tearing it off to hand over to me.
Events.Title: %playername%
